vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

term.name: House Committee on Education and Labor
House Committee on Science, Space, and Technology

bill.summary: This resolution elects specified Members to the following House Committees: (1) Education and Labor; (2) Financial Services; (3) Homeland Security; (4) Science, Space, and Technology; and (5) Small Business.
